#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1549
msgid "How to"
msgstr "方法"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1550
msgid "Boost revenue with bundled service packages"
msgstr "サービスをセット販売するコースで収益を向上させましょう"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1551
msgid ""
"Turn your services into high-value packages that customers love. Combine "
"multiple appointments into a single, discounted offer that drives bigger, "
"more confident purchases."
msgstr ""
"選ばれるサービスを、魅力的な「セットプラン」を作成しましょう。複数のメニュー"
"をまとめてお得なコースとして提供して、顧客満足度と収益を同時に高めましょう。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1552
msgid ""
"Increase sales volume by encouraging customers to book more appointments at "
"once"
msgstr "同時に複数の予約をすることをお客様に促すことで、売上を増加させます。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1553
msgid ""
"Flexible pricing lets you set a fixed package price and offer attractive "
"discounts"
msgstr ""
"コースに固定料金を設定し、お得な割引料金で提供して集客を強化しましょう。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1554
msgid ""
"Improved customer retention as clients return to use the remaining sessions "
"in their package"
msgstr ""
"コース機能を活用して、お客様のリピート率をアップ。残りの利用回数を消化するた"
"めに再来店を促すことで離脱防止に役立ちます。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1555
msgid "Manage shared resources with ease"
msgstr "共有の設備・備品を効率的に管理できます。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1556
msgid ""
"Create rooms, equipment, or other resources that can be shared across "
"employees, services, or locations, ensuring customers only see time slots "
"when everything they need is truly available."
msgstr ""
"スタッフ、サービス、または場所において共有可能な部屋、設備、その他の備品を作"
"成し、お客様が必要とするすべてのものが確実に利用可能な時間帯のみが表示される"
"ようする。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1557
msgid ""
"Avoid double-booking by automatically coordinating shared rooms, equipment, "
"or tools"
msgstr ""
"共有スペースや設備・備品の予約を自動で連携。ダブルブッキングを未然に防ぎ、ス"
"ムーズな運用を実現します。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1558
msgid ""
"Streamline operations with one central place to manage all resources across "
"your business"
msgstr ""
"あらゆる設備・備品を一元管理。業務を効率化し、スムーズな運営を実現します。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1559
msgid ""
"Deliver a smoother booking experience by showing customers only real, "
"available time slots"
msgstr ""
"リアルタイムの空き状況のみを表示することで、お客様に確実かつスムーズな予約体"
"験を提供しましょう。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1560
msgid "Boost revenue with valuable extras"
msgstr "収益を向上させる価値ある追加機能"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1561
msgid ""
"Offer optional or mandatory extras during the booking process - upsell "
"additional services, products, or experiences to enhance appointments and "
"delight your customers."
msgstr ""
"予約時に、任意または必須で追加オプション項目を設定して、追加サービスや商品、"
"特別な体験を提供することで、予約内容をより充実させ、お客様の満足度を高めるこ"
"とができます。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1562
msgid ""
"Increase revenue by encouraging customers to purchase additional services or "
"products"
msgstr ""
"追加サービスや商品の同時購入を促し、収益性を向上させます。予約プロセスの中"
"で、魅力的な追加オプション提示が可能です。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1563
msgid ""
"Customize offerings to match specific services and meet diverse client needs"
msgstr ""
"各サービス内容に合わせた個別設定が可能。お客様の多様な要望に柔軟に対応できま"
"す。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1564
msgid ""
"Enhance the customer experience with tailored add-ons that add convenience "
"and value"
msgstr ""
"カスタマイズされたアドオンで利便性と価値を付加し、お客様体験を向上させます"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1565
msgid "Effortless management for every location"
msgstr "あらゆる場所の管理を、ストレスフリーに。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1566
msgid ""
"Easily organize multiple business locations in one place, ensuring smooth "
"operations and a consistent booking experience no matter where your services "
"are offered."
msgstr ""
"複数拠点の管理を、これひとつで。どこでも変わらない、最高のご予約体験を。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1567
msgid ""
"Centralize scheduling across all branches for clearer, simpler management"
msgstr ""
"すべてのブランチにわたるスケジューリングを一元化し、より明確でシンプルな管理"
"を実現する"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1568
msgid ""
"Improve customer experience by letting clients choose the location that "
"suits them best"
msgstr ""
"お客様が場所を自由に選択できるようにして、アクセスの良さとお客様満足度を高め"
"ましょう。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1569
msgid ""
"Keep operations aligned with unified settings, availability, and resource "
"control"
msgstr "設定、空き状況、備品・設備管理を統一し、運用を最適化しましょう。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1570
msgid "Collect the information your business truly needs"
msgstr "ビジネスに真に必要な情報を収集する"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1571
msgid ""
"Build tailored forms across services, events, and customer profiles using "
"custom fields. Capture exactly the details you need with checkboxes, text "
"areas, and more, turning every booking and registration into a powerful "
"intake process."
msgstr ""
"カスタム項目を活用し、サービス、イベント、 お客様情報ごとに最適化されたフォー"
"ムを構築します。チェックボックスやテキストエリアなどで必要な詳細情報を正確に"
"収集し、あらゆる予約や登録を強力な情報収集プロセスへと変えます。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1572
msgid ""
"Customize every interaction by gathering the right information for services, "
"events, and customer records"
msgstr ""
"サービスやイベントの予約時のお客様に関する必要な情報を収集して、一人ひとりに"
"合わせた最適な対応を可能にします。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1573
msgid ""
"Keep your data organized and meaningful with structured fields that "
"standardize the information you collect"
msgstr "情報の入力形式を統一し、整理しやすく意味のあるデータ管理を実現します。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1574
msgid ""
"Enhance the customer experience with clear, intuitive forms designed around "
"your business needs"
msgstr ""
"お客様のビジネスニーズに合わせて設計された、明確で直感的なフォームでお客様体"
"験を向上させます"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1575
msgid "Automated invoices for a smoother payment experience"
msgstr "請求書の自動発行で、お支払いまでをよりスムーズに。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1576
msgid ""
"Automatically generate invoices for every booking, making payments easier, "
"more transparent, and fully streamlined for both you and your clients."
msgstr ""
"サービスやイベントに税金を自動計算して適用。正確な請求とスムーズなコンプライ"
"アンス対応を、すべての取引で実現します。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1577
msgid "Save time and reduce manual work with instant, auto-generated invoices"
msgstr "時間を節約し、手作業を減らす自動生成の即時請求書"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1578
msgid ""
"Improve accuracy and professionalism with consistent, clearly formatted "
"billing"
msgstr ""
"正確かつ統一感のある請求書作成機能で、業務のプロフェッショナル性を高めます。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1579
msgid ""
"Enhance client trust by providing transparent, documented payment details "
"for every booking"
msgstr ""
"一目でわかる支払い明細を提供することで、トラブルを防ぎ、信頼性を向上させま"
"す。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1580
msgid "Drive bookings with irresistible coupon offers"
msgstr "魅力的なクーポン特典で予約を促進しましょう"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1581
msgid ""
"Create unique coupon codes that customers can redeem during booking-offer "
"discounts or even free appointments to boost engagement, satisfaction, and "
"sales."
msgstr ""
"独自のクーポンコードを作成して、予約時に適用可能です。割引や無料セッションの"
"提供を通じて、お客様のリピート率と収益の向上を実現します。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1582
msgid ""
"Increase conversions by motivating customers with attractive, limited-time "
"deals"
msgstr ""
"魅力的な期間限定オファーでお客様の購買意欲を高め、コンバージョンを向上させま"
"しょう"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1583
msgid ""
"Flexible discount options let you set custom values or offer full-price "
"waivers"
msgstr ""
"柔軟な割引オプションにより、任意の金額設定から全額無料（100%オフ）まで、自由"
"自在に設定できます。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1584
msgid ""
"Enhance customer loyalty by rewarding clients with exclusive, personalized "
"offers"
msgstr ""
"お客様に合わせた専用のオファーを配信。特別感を提供することでお客様の愛着心を"
"高め、リピートを促します。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1585
msgid "Effortless tax management for every booking"
msgstr "予約ごとの税金計算も、これだけで完結。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1586
msgid ""
"Automatically calculate and apply taxes to your services and events, "
"ensuring accurate billing and hassle-free compliance with every transaction."
msgstr ""
"サービスやイベントに税金を自動計算して適用。正確な請求とスムーズなコンプライ"
"アンス対応を、すべての取引で実現します。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1587
msgid "Eliminate manual calculations with smart, automated tax application"
msgstr ""
"税金の自動適用により、手作業による計算の手間を排除。スマートな自動算出ロジッ"
"クで、常に正確な税額が反映されます。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1588
msgid "Ensure accurate billing by applying the correct tax rates every time"
msgstr ""
"正確な請求管理：適切な税率を自動で適用。あらゆる取引において正しい税率を算出"
"し、請求漏れや計算ミスのない正確な運用を実現します。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1589
msgid ""
"Stay compliant with ease through consistent, reliable tax handling across "
"your business"
msgstr ""
"ビジネス全体の税務処理を標準化。確実な対応で、コンプライアンス維持をスムーズ"
"に。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1590
msgid "Stay connected with WhatsApp notifications"
msgstr "WhatsApp通知でつながり続けましょう"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1591
msgid ""
"Keep customers and employees informed by sending appointment and event "
"notifications directly through WhatsApp - choose predefined messages or "
"customize your own for a personal touch."
msgstr ""
"WhatsAppを通じて直接予約やイベントの通知を送信し、顧客やスタッフに情報を提供"
"しましょう。あらかじめ用意されたメッセージを選択するか、独自のメッセージをカ"
"スタマイズして個別の対応が可能です。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1592
msgid ""
"Boost engagement by reaching clients instantly on a platform they use every "
"day"
msgstr ""
"お客様が普段から使い慣れたプラットフォームを通じた通知が、再来店のきっかけを"
"作ります。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1593
