#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1795
msgid "Create service"
msgstr "サービスを作成する"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1796
msgid ""
"Book time-based appointments with configurable durations, prices, and "
"availability."
msgstr "時間ベースの予約を、設定可能な所要時間、料金、空き状況で予約できます。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1797
msgid ""
"In Amelia, a “service” is a specific appointment-type offering your business "
"provides to clients - such as consultations, treatments, or classes - that "
"can be fully customized with its own name, duration, price, capacity, "
"availability, and extras, and booked online with assigned employees."
msgstr ""
"Ameliaにおける『サービス』とは、コンサルティング、施術、クラスなど、お客様に"
"提供する具体的な予約メニューのことです。名称、所要時間、料金、予約上限数、予"
"約可能日時、追加オプションなどを自由にカスタマイズでき、担当スタッフを割り当"
"ててオンライン予約を受け付けることができます。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1798
msgid "Create event"
msgstr "イベントを作成する"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1799
msgid "Create scheduled events with fixed dates, prices and capacities."
msgstr ""
"特定の日時、料金、定員を指定して、スケジュール設定されたイベントを作成する。"

#: src/Infrastructure/WP/Translations/LiteBackendStrings.php:1800
msgid ""
"In Amelia, an event is a booking-type offering designed for group activities "
"or multi-day occasions - such as workshops, conferences, tours, or training "
"series - that can be configured with its own schedule, capacity, pricing "
"structure and assigned staff."
msgstr ""
"Ameliaの「イベント」は、複数人での参加や複数日にまたがる予約（講座やツアーな"
"ど）に適した機能です。独自の開催期間、募集人数、料金設定、および担当者の割り"
"当てが可能です。"

